title: [m4rf] Heathen City [FUR]
description:
Hi all,

Heathen City is a serial graphic novel written by Alex Vance, illustrated by Ayato, Distasty, Krahnos, Charha and Fel.

Described as a modern, erotic thriller, Heathen City is an adult title with strong gay themes, graphic sex, strong language and violence. The gritty, contemporary setting and the sense of peril and isolation in an urban environment show the influence of works like Sin City and Blacksad. 

More info @: http://furry.wikia.com/wiki/Heathen_City
